00:46:26,200 --> 00:46:27,868
Hai.

805
00:46:27,952 --> 00:46:29,453
Aku rasa Johnny dah tukar fikiran.

806
00:46:40,173 --> 00:46:43,884
Aku tak percaya yang kau ada di sini lagi. Kau tak faham.

